snippet.title: Planetary Life - Trailer 2023 (Remake)
snippet.description:
Planetary Life is a planet, life and evolution simulation game.

🎮 Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2471970/Planetary_Life?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=trailer2

🌍 Discord server:
https://discord.gg/rN4KFgkVu8

🔥 Follow on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/pitxardo
https://twitter.com/sotenbox

Full planet and climate simulation.
A game about life evolution and survival simulation.
From cells to creatures and monsters to civilizations.
Everything procedurally generated.

#evolution #simulation #devlog #ecosystem #game #ai
